{"about_the_game":"Originally released in 1989, this dirtbike simulator brought all the fun and challenge of motocross to home computers. Now, relive those days in this remastered emulated version.<br><br>Contains all the versions originally created for the Amiga, Commodore 64, Amstrad CPC, and ZX Spectrum computers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>Make your way through a series of hazardous motocross courses against the clock. Careful control of speed, angle, and gearing is required to stay upright and moving. Perform tricky wheelies to clear divots, and control your bike precisely to land safely after long jumps.<br><br><br>This enhanced version introduces a number of modern features to this retro classic, including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Saving/loading the game at any point<br></li><li> Support for most modern game controllers<br></li><li> Full control remapping<br></li><li> Image scaling and smoothing options</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1682413005","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363510/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1682413005","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363510/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1682413005","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363510/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1682413005","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Originally released in 1989, this dirtbike simulator brought all the fun and challenge of motocross to home computers. Now, relive those days in this remastered emulated version.<br><br>Contains all the versions originally created for the Amiga, Commodore 64, Amstrad CPC, and ZX Spect